des:
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your smart devices - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap, or Echo Show.
Connect Alexa to your Amcrest products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our “Amcrest” app in the Android or iOS app market;
2. Register one Amcrest account in our "Amcrest" app;
3. You need to have some Amcrest devices in hand;
4. Configure these devices in our “Amcrest” app and assign appropriate names to your devices, which will be used in "Amcrest" skills;
5. Download the Amazon "Alexa" app from the Android, iOS, or Amazon app market;
6. Configure Echo with the "Alexa" app;
7. Search for the "Amcrest" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
8. Click to enable the skill for "Amcrest", and you'll be navigated to the Amcrest login page;
9. Input your Amcrest account username and password, and you'll be redirected to the success page;
10. Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, Show Camera"
“Alexa, Hide the Camera"
“Alexa, Stop the Camera”
